I"´<h1 id="company"><strong>Company</strong></h1>

<h2 id="create">Create</h2>
<p><strong>Step-1</strong>:  Click on <strong>New-&gt; Company</strong>. Company form will appear.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_0.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-2</strong>: Fill the details in <strong>Basic</strong>, <strong>Config</strong> and <strong>Logo</strong> tab.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_1.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_2.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_3.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-3</strong>: Click on <strong>GST Reg</strong> tab and click on <strong>Add New</strong> button to register GSTIN number of company. The blank row appears in GST Reg tab. Fill the details in this row and click on <strong>Save</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_4.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<h2 id="list">List</h2>

<p>Click on <strong>Master</strong> menu and select <strong>Company</strong>. Company list will appear.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_5.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<h2 id="edit">Edit</h2>

<p><strong>Step-1</strong>: Select the company from company list and right click on it. Click on <strong>Edit Company</strong> option. Company details will open.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_6.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>Step-2</strong>: Edit the details and click on <strong>Save</strong>.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Note: You can edit company by right click on campus and select edit company.</p>
</blockquote>
